high_descs: Turn right, take a step forward, turn left, walk straight beside a sidetable with a microwave to reach a diningtable.
Pick up an apple from the diningtable.
Walk back where you came from but stop by the microwave.
Put the apple inside the microwave.
Return to the diningtable but approach it from the opposite side.
Pick up a knife from the diningtable.
Go back to the microwave.
Cut an apple in the microwave with the knife.
anns.task_desc: Using the knife, cut the apple inside the microwave.

high_descs: Turn left and go straight towards the wall. Then, hang left and walk straight into the room and turn to the dining table on your right.
Pick up apple from the dining table.
Turn around and make a straight turn before proceeding to turn left towards the microwave.
Place apple on the microwave.
Go straight towards the wall and then walk straight into the room, turning to the dining table on your right.
Pick up knife from the dining table.
Turn around and make a straight turn before proceeding to turn left towards the microwave.
Place apple on the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Obtaining knife, apple from various locations and arranging them in a microwave.

high_descs: Turn right, move forward, turn left, move forward from the dining table
Take on the apple from the dining table
Turn around the left, move forward, turn right, move forward, turn right from the microwave
Open the microwave, place in the apple, close the door from the microwave
Turn right, move forward, turn left, move forward, turn left, move forward, turn left from the dining table
Take on the knife from the dining table
Turn left, move forward, turn right, move forward, turn right, move forward, turn right from the microwave
Open the microwave, cut in the apple, close the door from the microwave
anns.task_desc: Take on the apple from the dining table, open the microwave, cut in the apple.
